Ghost Wanderer v0.0.3
by Jad Hachem

How long can your ghost wander among hostile ghosts?


INTRODUCTION
------------

Ghost Wanderer is a game I wrote for fun and to practice my coding skills.
The player controls a ghost that wanders around in a rectangular area
and tries to avoid bumping into other wandering ghosts.


REQUIREMENTS
------------

- gcc >= 4.7
- SFML >= 2.0
- Linux or Mac OS X


INSTALLATION & RUNNING
----------------------

To install the program, you simply need to compile it by running:
	$ make
in the root directory of the project.

To run the program, simply run the executable:
	$ ./ghost-wanderer
from the root directory of the project (after compiling).


INSTRUCTIONS
------------

You can find instructions on how to play the game
in the MANUAL text file that came with this program.


